**Adding a New Command:**
{% if cli_framework == 'cobra' %}
1. Add a `newXCmd() *cobra.Command` function in `internal/cli/cli.go`
2. Register it with `rootCmd.AddCommand(newXCmd())` in `NewRootCmd()`
{% elif cli_framework == 'urfave-cli' %}
1. Add a `*cli.Command` entry to the `Commands` slice in `NewApp()`
{% else %}
